des: In this skill, Columbus Crew Chants allows you to listen to the recorded fan section chants that happen during the game, inside the stadium. This way you can feel a part of the fan section with Alexa. You can listen to all twelve available chants and then repeat, you can stop at any time, or stop every five chants
